  "description": {
    "short": "Meet colleagues, peers, and experts across your org wherever you are",
    "full": "Get Connected helps virtual and distributed teams grow professionally and feel a sense of inclusion by facilitating the spontaneous chats and meetups that traditionally occur in physical offices. Meet colleagues randomly, discover peers with similar skills and backgrounds, and get help from experts. This app can be easily extended with Microsoft Power Platform to meet your org's needs."
